# level 3 intermediate task tracking

> **tldr:** this document provides structured task tracking guidelines for level 3 (intermediate feature) tasks, using visual tracking elements and clear checkpoints.

## 🔍 task tracking workflow

```mermaid
graph td
    start["task start"] --> init["📋 initialize<br>task entry"]
    init --> struct["🏗️ create task<br>structure"]
    struct --> track["📊 progress<br>tracking"]
